(11, 'Contemporary Classics', 'Celery, Lemon Wedge (Optional)', 'N/A', 'https://iba-world.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IBA-CC-03-Bloody-Marry-scaled.jpg', 'https://iba-world.com/bloody-mary/', 'Stir gently all the ingredients in a mixing glass with ice, pour into rocks glass.', 'Bloody Mary', 'If requested served with ice, pour into highball glass.', 5),
