(56, 'New Era Drinks', 'Garnish with lemon or orange zest with cherry.', 'N/A', 'https://iba-world.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IBA-NE-12-NewYorkSour.jpg', 'Bourbon or Rye Whiskey - 60 ml, Simple Syrup - 22.5 ml, Fresh Lemon Juice - 30 ml, Egg White - Few Drops, Red wine (Shiraz or Malbech) - 15 ml', 'https://iba-world.com/new-york-sour/', 'Pour all ingredients into the shaker. Shake vigorously with ice. Strain into a chilled rocks glass filled with ice. Float the wine on top.', 'New York Sour', 'N/A', 8),
(57, 'New Era Drinks', 'Garnish with mint springs.', 'N/A', 'https://iba-world.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IBA-NE-13-Old-Cuban.jpg', 'Mint Leaves - 6/8 pcs, Aged Rum - 45 ml, Fresh Lime Juice - 22.5 ml, Simple Syrup - 30 ml, Angostura Bitters - 2 Dashes, Brut Champagne or Prosecco - 60 ml', 'https://iba-world.com/old-cuban/', 'Pour all ingredients into cocktail shaker except the wine, shake well with ice, strain into chilled elegant cocktail glass. Top up with the sparkling wine.', 'Old Cuban', 'N/A', 7),
(58, 'The Unforgettables', 'Garnish with an orange slice or zest, and a cocktail cherry.', 'N/A', 'https://iba-world.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IBA-TU-21-Old-Fashioned.jpg', 'Bourbon or Rye Whiskey - 45 ml, Sugar Cube - 1, Angostura Bitters - Few Dashes, Plain Water - Few Dashes', 'https://iba-world.com/old-fashioned/', 'Place sugar cube in old fashioned glass and saturate with bitter, add few dashes of plain water. Muddle until dissolved. Fill the glass with ice cubes and add whiskey. Stir gently.', 'Old Fashioned', 'N/A', 9),
(59, 'New Era Drinks', 'Garnish with a slice of lime.', 'N/A', 'https://iba-world.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IBA-NE-14-Paloma.jpg', '100% Agave Tequila - 50 ml, Fresh Lime - 5 ml, Salt - A pinch, Pink Grapefruit Soda - 100 ml', 'https://iba-world.com/paloma/', 'Poor the tequila into a highball glass, squeeze the lime juice. Add ice and salt, fill up pink grapefruit soda. Stir gently.', 'Paloma', 'N/A', 9),
